title: 187. Let It Go
itunes:title: 187. Let It Go
description: The winner's circle has no place for people who compete to be the best victim. In today's episode, Andy talks about the problem with people consistently looking for sympathy online, how to recognize when you're playing the victim and how you can flip the switch to make forward progress by letting go of the past.
